---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us">
    <main class="site-main">
        <section style="background-color: var(--secondary-color); color: #fff; padding: 60px 20px; text-align: center;">
            <h1 style="font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: #fff;">About RaxPublications</h1>
            <p style="font-size: 18px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">Dedicated to the advancement of global knowledge and technical excellence.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="section-wrapper" style="max-width: 1000px; margin: 60px auto; padding: 0 20px;">
            <div style="background: #fff; padding: 40px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #eee; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
                <h2 style="font-size: 32px; color: var(--heading-color); margin-bottom: 20px;">Our Mission</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; color: #444; margin-bottom: 30px;">
                    RaxPublications was founded with a singular vision: to bridge the gap between complex academic research and global accessibility. We believe that groundbreaking research in Science, Engineering, and Artificial Intelligence should be rigorously peer-reviewed yet rapidly disseminated to the academic community and industry professionals alike.
                </p>

                <h2 style="font-size: 32px; color: var(--heading-color); margin-bottom: 20px;">Our Editorial Process</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; color: #444; margin-bottom: 30px;">
                    Integrity is at the heart of our publishing model. Every manuscript submitted to our journals undergoes a stringent double-blind peer review process. Our editorial board consists of highly respected academics and industry leaders who ensure that all published work meets the highest standards of methodological rigor and originality.
                </p>

                <h2 style="font-size: 32px; color: var(--heading-color); margin-bottom: 20px;">Open Access Commitment</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; color: #444;">
                    We are staunch advocates of the Open Access movement. By publishing with RaxPublications, authors ensure their work is immediately and freely available worldwide, maximizing the visibility, citation potential, and impact of their research.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
